e opportunity to those awaiting regression in the country\u2019s political spectrum, the Chief Minister argued.\n\nParty leaders Laxman Lal Karn, Ram Naresh Yadav and others expressed their opinions while claiming that the intraparty feuds in the Nepal Communist Party resulted in a democratic crisis.","title":"'HoR dissolution promotes political instability' - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/11/155603/","video":[]}
